Node.js
```
import { Apideck } from '@apideck/node'
const apideck = new Apideck({
apiKey: 'YOUR_API_KEY',
appId: 'YOUR_APP_ID',
consumerId: 'user-123'
})
// List drives from any connected file storage platform
const response = await apideck.file-storage.drivesAll()
// Returns normalized data regardless of the underlying platform
console.log(response.data)
// [
// { id: '123', ...
},
// { id: '456', ...
}
// ]
// Works the same for Xero, QuickBooks, NetSuite, etc.
```

# Google Drive Folders API - Sync Folders Data - Apideck
created: 2024-01-15, last updated: 2026-06-01, [Read more](https://www.apideck.com/integrations/google-drive/folders)

Sync permissioned folders data with Google Drive through Apideck's unified API.
...
Create, Get, Update, Delete operations available through our unified API
list
get
create
update
delete
...
import { Apideck } from '@apideck/unify'
const apideck = new Apideck({
apiKey: process.env.APIDECK_API_KEY,
appId: 'YOUR_APP_ID',
consumerId: 'YOUR_CONSUMER_ID'
})
// List folders from Google Drive
const result = await apideck.file-storage.folders.list({
serviceId: 'google-drive'
})
for await (const page of result) {
console.log(page)
}
// Returns unified folders data
```

